---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of service for Be Balanced Counseling website.">
  <section class="py-24 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto prose">
      <h1 class="text-4xl text-charcoal mb-12 text-center">Terms of Service</h1>

      <div class="text-charcoal-light space-y-8">
        <p>
          <em>Last updated: [Date]</em>
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-charcoal mt-12 mb-6">Website Content</h2>
        <p>
          The content on this website is for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional mental health advice, diagnosis, or treatment.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-charcoal mt-12 mb-6">No Therapist-Client Relationship</h2>
        <p>
          Using this website, subscribing to the newsletter, submitting a question, or purchasing courses does not create a therapist-client relationship. A therapist-client relationship is only established through a formal agreement after an initial consultation.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-charcoal mt-12 mb-6">Crisis Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          This website is not designed to address mental health crises. If you are in crisis, please call 988 (Suicide & Crisis Lifeline), text HOME to 741741 (Crisis Text Line), or go to your nearest emergency room.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-charcoal mt-12 mb-6">Courses and Digital Products</h2>
        <p>
          Digital products purchased through this site are for personal use only. They are educational tools and are not therapy. Refunds are available within 14 days of purchase.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-charcoal mt-12 mb-6">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about these terms, please <a href="/contact" class="text-sage hover:text-sage-dark">contact us</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
